
<div class="container flex-grow-1" id="homepage">
  <div class="details-section">
    <h1 class="name" data-aos="out" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-top">Emily Hoult</h1>
    <div class="title-box col-7 p-0" data-aos="out" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-top">
      <p class="title">UI/UX Designer & Frontend Developer</p>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="cv-btn" data-aos="out" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-top">Download CV</button>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex svgs circle" data-aos="out" data-aos-anchor-placement="bottom-top">
    <%= image_tag("circle.svg", class: "circle-svg") %>
    <%= image_tag("p-dot-1.svg", class: "p-dot-1") %>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section d-flex flex-wrap">

    <div class="row p-0" data-aos="out" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-top">
      <h1 class="col-12 about" id="about">About</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row p-0">
      <div class="col-7 p-0">
        <p class="pr-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-sine">
          Hey, I’m Emily. I’m a Junior UI/UX Designer and Frontend Developer passionate about designing and building seamless, intuitive and elegant solutions. I’m a fast learner and problem solver with a strong eye for detail. I have a background in Fashion Merchandising and E-Commerce where I learned to understand consumer wants and needs and how to react to them.
          <br>
          <br>
        </p>
        <p class="pr-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-sine">
          When I'm not behind my laptop, you can find me taking lots of photos of <a href="/photos" class="link link--line">the sky and gazing at the moon.</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-5 p-0">
       <%= image_tag("emilyhoult.jpg", class: "emilyhoult") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="d-flex svgs triangle">
    <%= image_tag("triangle.svg", class: "triangle-svg") %>
    <%= image_tag("p-dot-2.svg", class: "p-dot-2") %>
  </div>

  <div class="skills-section d-flex">
    <h2 class="skills col-12">Skills & Tools</h2>
    <div class="col-4 web-li">
      <div class="d-flex mb-4">
        <%= image_tag("square.svg", class: "square-svg") %>
        <h5 class="m-0">Web Development</h5>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>HTML, CSS, SCSS</li>
        <li>JavaScript, Bootstrap</li>
        <li>Ruby, Rails, SQL</li>
        <li>APIs, Scraping</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 ui-li">
      <div class="d-flex mb-4">
        <%= image_tag("square.svg", class: "square-svg") %>
        <h5 class="m-0">UI/UX Design</h5>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>User Research & Testing</li>
        <li>User Journeys & Flows</li>
        <li>Wireframing, Prototyping</li>
        <li>Style Guides, Mood Boards</li>
        <li>Logos, Branding</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 software-li">
      <div class="d-flex mb-4">
        <%= image_tag("square.svg", class: "square-svg") %>
        <h5 class="m-0">Software & Tools</h5>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>Sketch, Adobe XD, Figma</li>
        <li>Git, GitHub, Heroku</li>
        <li>Microstrategy, Tableau</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="work-section" id="work">
